<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空他们为躲避大火，跑到山下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“红孩儿的火太厉害了。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要被烤熟了！”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净抬头看着山顶。“现在火变小了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”悟空看着最后几缕烟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们现在回去的话，他还会喷火。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要水。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他再喷火，我们就可以把火浇灭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空点头说道：“你们在这里等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道谁能帮我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空迅速跳到空中飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，他和东海龙王一起回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空向八戒和悟净介绍了东海龙王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以呼风唤雨。”龙王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们到山上叫红孩儿出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一喷火，我就下一场大暴雨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王飞到空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空他们再一次来到红孩儿的洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“红孩儿，开门！”悟空用力敲洞门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞门打开了，红孩儿跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上放了唐僧！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不放！”红孩儿叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用拳头打了一下自己的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鼻孔里又冒出了烟，嘴里喷出了火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙王！”悟空高叫，“快下雨！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天空中乌云密布，雷声阵阵，下起了大雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，大火并没有熄灭，反而越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>烟雾更浓了。悟空不停地咳嗽，呼吸困难。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他捂住了脸。他看见八戒和悟净向山下跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空想要靠近洞门，但烟实在太浓了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他被一块石头绊倒了，从山的一边跌了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>扑通！悟空掉到了河里，漂到了河岸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不停地咳嗽喘息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净迅速跑到了悟空身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，你没事吧？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没事。”悟空说。他又咳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那火不是普通的火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喷水反而会让火变得更大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”八戒说，“那一定是三昧真火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们现在怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧还在红孩儿的洞里呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去找观音菩萨帮忙。”悟空说着站起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你休息一下。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你吸了太多烟。我去找观音菩萨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又咳了起来。“好，八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马上去找观音菩萨。不能打瞌睡！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，红孩儿正坐在他的山顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的火很厉害。”他自言自语地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们现在一定死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿拍拍自己的肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好，我现在饿了。我要去煮唐僧了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当红孩儿站起来的时候，他看见天上有什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是猪八戒！”红孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他为什么往南飞呢？”红孩儿想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！观音菩萨住在南海普陀山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猪八戒一定是要去求她帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要拦住他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿快速念了个咒。他全身发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，红孩儿看上去就跟观音菩萨一模一样了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒驾着云正快速向南飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见观音菩萨朝自己飞来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨！”八戒笑着大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太巧了。我正要去找您！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>